description:
• This course teaches you how to use the law of attraction to help you lose weight and achieve your ideal weight, health and fitness levels.
  • You'll learn how to become a match for your ideal weight and create a positive mindset to support you as you lose weight.
  • You'll find a mix of video's, audio's and text lecture in this course as well as printouts a resources.
  • This is an ideal course for anyone wanting to lose weight, especially for those who have struggled with weight for some time. The mindset shift is important for lasting weight loss.
  • Please note that this is not a diet or exercise plan.
title: Law of Attraction Weight Loss
